name: Fcmdemo

# FCM Demo 
Firebase push notification, it is advance version of GCM. We can send message though firebase console and php code also. 

We create this project to explore Firebase. we have some other interesting feature of firebase  which is interesting and useful in co-corporate for development. 

##here are some important feature of firebase 
  1. Firebase social authentication. 

2.  Firebase real time database 

3. firebase analytics 

4. firebase crashlytics 

## Developer Contributor 

We want need contributor who  can explore firebase
